| Feature               | `driver.close()`                       | `driver.quit()`                                    |
| --------------------- | -------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Purpose**           | Current browser window close karta hai | Entire browser session close karta hai             |
| **Windows/Tabs**      | Sirf active tab/window close hota hai  | Sabhi windows/tabs close ho jate hain              |
| **WebDriver Session** | Session active reh sakta hai           | WebDriver session completely terminate ho jata hai |
| **Usage**             | Jab ek specific window close karna ho  | Jab pura browser close karna ho                    |

---------------------------------------
driver.close() closes only the current browser window, 
while driver.quit() closes all browser windows and terminates the entire WebDriver session.
